OL,3,CGalicia: The community where women
OL,4,Cdominate the fishing industry
OL,6,FI travelled to Cambados, a town on the
OL,7,FAtlantic coast, to meet some of the
OL,8,Fwomen and hear about their pride in
OL,9,Fthis work which they fiercely protect
OL,10,Ffor the next generation.
OL,12,FMany of their methods are unchanged in
OL,13,Fhundreds of years, but what is
OL,14,Fchanging is the climate around them.
OL,16,FShell fish stocks have been hit hard
OL,17,Fby extreme weather events including
OL,18,Fheatwaves and heavy rainfall.
