OL,3,CGalicia: The community where women
OL,4,Cdominate the fishing industry
OL,6,FData from the Galician government
OL,7,Fshows numbers at the end of 2023 were
OL,8,Fjust 15 percent of what they were the
OL,9,Fyear before, with all four of the main
OL,10,Fspecies of shell fish harvested in the
OL,11,Farea now struggling to recover.
OL,13,FMaria Jose Cacabelos who is the
OL,14,Fpresident of Guimatur, the Association
OL,15,Fof Sea Women of Cambados, told me that
OL,16,Flast winter was very hard, due to
OL,17,Fheavy rainfall.
