OL,3,CGalicia: The community where women
OL,4,Cdominate the fishing industry
OL,6,F"Salinity dropped and a lot of
OL,7,Fshellfish died," she said, but added
OL,8,Fthat jobs in contact with nature are
OL,9,Fvulnerable to the weather.
OL,11,F"It happens to farmers, sailors and
OL,12,Fshell fish harvesters. It depends a
OL,13,Flot on the climate."
OL,15,FThe mariscadoras have a bond that runs
OL,16,Fthrough their veins, with friendships
OL,17,Fbuilt on the muddy sand at low tide
OL,18,Fwhere they gather shellfish.
OL,20,FThe skill and value of the work
OL,21,Fmustn't be underestimated.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
