OL,3,CGalicia: The community where women
OL,4,Cdominate the fishing industry
OL,6,FTraditionally, their income supported
OL,7,Fthat of the men in the family, paying
OL,8,Ffor the day to day costs of running a
OL,9,Fhousehold, while the wages from the
OL,10,Ffishermen covered bigger expenses.
OL,12,FSometimes though, the shell-
OL,13,Ffisherwomen provide what is the only
OL,14,Fincome for families, when the weather
OL,15,Fis too bad to go out to sea.
