OL,3,CGalicia: The community where women
OL,4,Cdominate the fishing industry
OL,6,FThe job continues to appeal to younger
OL,7,Fwomen who are juggling modern life.
OL,8,FWorking around the tides and
OL,9,Fregulations to protect fish stocks,
OL,10,Fmeans each "shift" is usually around
OL,11,Ffour hours long, which, in turn,
OL,12,Fallows time to manage other
OL,13,Fresponsibilities at home.
OL,15,FMelissa, who was taught by her mother
OL,16,FVictoria, tells me how, as a teenager,
OL,17,Fcollecting shellfish would help pay
OL,18,Ffor a night out.
