OL,3,CGalicia: The community where women
OL,4,Cdominate the fishing industry
OL,6,FNow she fits the job around looking
OL,7,Fafter her son, and helping her husband
OL,8,Frun a bar.
OL,10,FVictoria though worries for the
OL,11,Ffuture, having witnessed over decades
OL,12,Fthe changes in the climate and also
OL,13,Fthe environmental threat from other
OL,14,Findustries to their profession.
OL,16,FRecently some of the women have been
OL,17,Finvolved in demonstrations against a
OL,18,Fpulp company, who plan to build a new
OL,19,Ffactory in Galicia.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
