OL,3,CGalicia: The community where women
OL,4,Cdominate the fishing industry
OL,6,FVictoria swears she will fight until
OL,7,Fit's "kicked out" and she will "fight
OL,8,Flike a champion."
OL,10,FOn meeting these women, I had the
OL,11,Fstrong impression that this way of
OL,12,Flife won't be stamped out easily.
OL,14,FIt was clear to me that their grit,
OL,15,Fdetermination and passion could very
OL,16,Fwell save and protect it, as losing it
OL,17,Fwould mean more than just a loss of
OL,18,Fincome, it would be the loss of their
OL,19,Fsense of identity.
